ne Survivors gives you the freedom to shape your gameplay with over 350 active skills across multiple characters. Whether you crave raw power or strategic mastery, you can craft your perfect build and dominate the battlefield your way. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHALLENGE TITANS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/Bosses_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for battle against titanic bosses that will push your skills to the limit. These massive foes will demand all your skill and strategy to overcome their overwhelming power. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MASSIVE SKILL TREE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/SkillTree_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The skill tree is vast and diverse, allowing each character to stand out with their own ultimate abilities. Customize your experience, enhance your playstyle, and enjoy a unique journey with every hero you choose. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNIQUE PLAYABLE CHARACTERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/Characters_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With 18 distinct characters to master, Soulstone Survivors offers unparalleled variety. Each Void Hunter comes equipped with unique weapons, abilities, and specializations, giving you endless ways to conquer your foes. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR BUILD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/Runes_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from dozens of powerful runes to shape your path from the start, and create unstoppable, game-breaking synergies by combining them with hundreds of passive skills. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CRAFT POWERFUL WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/Craft_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forge unique weapons for your Void Hunters and unlock powerful new abilities, allowing you to push your characters\u2019 playstyles even further, giving you endless ways to fine-tune your approach. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAPS AND GAME MODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/extras/Maps_Gif.gif?t=1737464931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re in control of your challenges. Select from numerous curses and different game modes to ramp up the difficulty and explore new ways to test your mastery in every run. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SPECIAL THANKS TO THE COMMUNITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We are a tiny team that chose to stay independent and continue developing the game we love, and would like to thank each and every one of you that has helped us along the way! Soulstone Survivors would not be the same without your feedback! </p>","developers":["Game Smithing Limited"],"dlc":[2202970],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066020/header.jpg?t=1737464931","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Linux/X11<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.5Ghz or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<